7T01:41:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b4e76513ee94c7d7d6f6d25ecb0ae4ecc5ebc5a8","tid":1630643,"uid":218298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T01:43:47.000Z","msg":"「認真」各位手足 借東風啊！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1629930\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1629930</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n麻煩幫手推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dad2561d211478eb2a8cdc75c0469fd778cbb355","tid":1630643,"uid":51418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cf772dd9ea78db6a466d74771cfa5b34c3491f47","tid":1630643,"uid":294783,"like":47,"dislike":2,"score":45,"citedBy":8,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:09:29.000Z","msg":"顯咗啦!<br />\n乜冇人睇到咩?<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/10/07/000905_017a6e3e60c682d464bbf9a17962c350.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F10%2F07%2F000905_017a6e3e60c682d464bbf9a17962c350.jpg&h=6b004ccc&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T02:15:56.000Z","msg":"手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9300cefdf79eb978ad61f1c8f5561627e45bbcd7","tid":1630643,"uid":180317,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T02:17:05.000Z","msg":"呢排成日夜晚行雷閃電，我真心信係有人係到鬥法中架..."},{"pid":"3e81ce6109d3accf26ecbc85ab50e94976c2f57e","tid":1630643,"uid":19215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T02:21:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a20993cc3f88973c6676e9fdcfcbf7a4b81d0989","tid":1630643,"uid":266342,"like":69,"dislike":0,"score":69,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T02:28:00.000Z","msg":"其實果斷路鬼封咗成20幾年啦<br />\n咁多年都相安無事唔會有車係會駛左入去果一段路到<br />\n你諗下每一年打風話封露天路段<br />\n咪又係荔景做尾站<br />\n點解會冇事而家會有事呀<br />\n<br />\n其實嗰班死咗嘅兄弟係實係好慘㗎<br />\n生唔見人死唔見屍仲要冇埋名<br />\n你諗下個個都係十幾廿歲嘅後生仔<br />\n其實好多嘢都未面對過突然間就冇咗條命<br />\n最重要就係眼白白見到自己死咗自己個肉身俾啲咁嘅人掉咗唔知去邊度<br />\n咁都算仲要個魂魄俾人封住咗係個地下行唔到上嚟<br />\n真係可以理解到佢哋好慘怨氣好大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但系我想有機會同佢地講你哋都要加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔會有人唔記得你哋所犧牲嘅一切<br />\n唔好覺得自己孤單<br />\n即使係去咗另一個世界大把人都係會與你同行㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af78d0a3c6873d1667f1948cd33adb39cc93c8a5","tid":1630643,"uid":41035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T02:30:02.000Z","msg":"重陽呀嘛"},{"pid":"d8d348e38a71bdb968bdb4053e625b2d316f9de8","tid":1630643,"uid":186316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cf772dd9ea78db6a466d74771cfa5b34c3491f47","tid":1630643,"uid":294783,"like":47,"dislike":2,"score":45,"citedBy":8,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:09:29.000Z","msg":"顯咗啦!<br />\n乜冇人睇到咩?<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/10/07/000905_017a6e3e60c682d464bbf9a17962c350.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F10%2F07%2F000905_017a6e3e60c682d464bbf9a17962c350.jpg&h=6b004ccc&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T02:35:28.000Z","msg":"係個女仔？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4a5b73c60bb6704e17ae8ad120dadc9aa73bdbb","tid":1630643,"uid":10630,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"c0592fd6a59bc9e4c49e1a0860860e0512c738b1","tid":1630643,"uid":149973,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"b7845ea8a72b7d0e3707a21a7d055f12ccdad9c3","tid":1630643,"uid":36058,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"41dfd401fa2e0c7abd0f5d17757d16157ce8f3bb","tid":1630643,"uid":294783,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:15:56.000Z","msg":"喂!係咪我睇錯呀?幫下眼望望唔該!"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T01:09:57.000Z","msg":"你睇到啲咩？"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T01:16:38.00